&lt;h1 id="how-to-work-hard"&gt;How to Work Hard&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;June 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It might not seem there&amp;rsquo;s much to learn about how to work hard. Anyone who&amp;rsquo;s been to school knows what it entails, even if they chose not to do it. There are 12 year olds who work amazingly hard. And yet when I ask if I know more about working hard now than when I was in school, the answer is definitely yes.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>